# HOMEPAGE - must be first rule (Netlify: first match wins)
/  /index.html  200

# Non-www to www canonical
https://chicagofleetwraps.com/*  https://www.chicagofleetwraps.com/:splat  301!

# Static files
/robots.txt    /robots.txt    200
/sitemap.xml   /sitemap.xml   200
/blog-feed.xml /blog-feed.xml 200
